The February 2025 Revelation:
On February 13, 2025, US Congressman Scott Perry claimed during a congressional hearing that USAID funded terrorist organizations including Boko Haram, ISIS, Al-Qaeda, and ISIS Khorasan, alleging that $697 million annually plus cash shipments funded Madrasas, terrorist training camps, and these groups Modern GhanaVerivafrica. This was stated on the record, in an official congressional hearing.
